*.pem
# Exception: the vendored Russian Trusted Root CA (TRD.9.1.1, INV-11) is a PUBLIC
# certificate — the investex venue-client TLS trust anchor — and MUST ship. Every
# other *.pem (private keys/secrets) stays ignored. Negation is surgical (verified).
!echo/apps/investex/priv/certs/russian_trusted_root_ca.pem

